truffle commands


truffle init 		>to get/create project like structre in local
truffle create contract <name>		> to create a contract.sol in local under contracts folder
truffle compile		> to compile the code


create a 2_deploy_contracts.js in migrations folder 

##########
var HelloWorld=artifacts.require (“./HelloWorld.sol”);
module.exports = function(deployer) {
      deployer.deploy(HelloWorld);
}
###########

use the above block of code to start deploying

truffle-config.js file 

########
module.exports = 
{
  networks:
  {
    development:
    {
      host: "localhost",
      port: 8545,
      network_id: "*"
    }
  }
};

############



truffle migrate >> making the deployment transaction

